 Syntax:  .sing <lyrics>   or   %<lyrics>

Results:  Allows you to sing your own merry little tune. Toot your own 
          horn. Whatever. If you like this command, thank Cygnus, if you 
          hate it, yell at Siglite.

Example:  If Cygnus types -->  %Oceans apart, day after day.
          People in the same room will see..
           Cygnus <singing slong> Oceans apart, day after day.

